14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 481, as
15 amended by Section 1, Chapter 283, O.S.L. 2024 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024,
16 Section 481), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 481. A State Board of Medical Licensure and Supervision
18 hereinafter referred to as the "Board", is hereby re-created, to
19 continue until July 1, 2025 2030, in accordance with the provisions
20 of the Oklahoma Sunset Law. The Board shall be composed of seven
21 (7) allopathic physicians licensed to practice medicine in this
22 state and represent the public and four (4) lay members. The
23 physician members of the Board shall be graduates of legally
24 chartered medical schools recognized by the Oklahoma State Regents
